cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper discusses deep learning-based methods for video anomaly detection, which involves computer vision and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised and semi-supervised learning, which falls under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of spatio-temporal anomaly detection, which falls under the categories of cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
